RHQ Agent Plugin Plugin

 Welcome to the RHQ Agent Plugin Plugin documentation.

 <<Plugin Plugin?>>

 Yes. Plugin Plugin: a Maven Plugin to help you build RHQ Agent Plugins.

 <<Great. But I know nothing about RHQ Agent Plugings...>>

 Then you'll want to read the {{{https://docs.jboss.org/author/display/RHQ/Plugins+-+Getting+Started}Getting Started with RHQ Agent Plugins}} wiki page first.
 You can also checkout the {{{http://www.redhat.com/f/pdf/Write_A_Plugin_WP_web.pdf}How to write a plugin for JBoss ON and RHQ Guide}} (PDF) -
 or the more up to date version {{{https://github.com/pilhuhn/misc_writing/tree/master/HowToWriteAnRhqPlugin}How to write a plugin}}.

* Available features

  * {{{./packaging.html}Packaging}}

  * {{{./validating.html}Validation}}

  * {{{./deploying.html}Deployment to a local RHQ Server (dev-container)}}

  * {{{./uploading.html}Upload to to a remote RHQ Server}}

  * {{{./executing-cli.html}CLI script or command execution}}

  * {{{./setting-up-test-plugin-container.html}Standalone Plugin Container setup for integration tests}}

